# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMRSE_00000163> (response to a question asking process)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMRSE_00000163> "Note that not all responses to a question asking process are answers. For example, a refusal to answer is not an answer. A refusal to answer is also not a specified output of the question asking process since it does not acheive the objective of asking the question, which is to get an answer."@en)
