AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMRSE_00000507> "A gender identity datum resulting from a gender identification process in which ‘non binary’ is selected based on the participant's subjective sense of gender."@en)
