AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMRSE_00000507> "William Hogan"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMRSE_00000507> "Alternatively: A gender identity datum stating that a person's subjective sense of gender is non-binary.)

Examples of usage: ‘Non-binary’, ‘Trigender’, ‘Agender’, ‘Genderfluid’, ‘2’ (intended to refer to a non-binary gender role)"@en)
